<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>731</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ nǐ ràng dà de jiàn lì zài dà shuǐ zhī shàng, nǐ yòng zhì huì pù zhāng qióng cāng.
 nǐ ràng yún duǒ zài kōng zhōng piāo fú, ràng rén lèi yōng yǒu yī gè tài yáng.
 dú yī zhēn shén zào wàn wù cì wǔ gǔ nǐ gěi rén lèi sòng lái zhù fú.
 zhǔ yé hé huá wǒ men jìng bài nǐ, nǐ shì quán de dú yī zhī zhǔ.</lyrics>
<title>zhǔ yé hé huá wǒ men jìng bài nǐ 迦南731</title>
</song>